sources.title: Dark Vengeance | Full Movie | Steven Seagal Action | True Justice Series
sources.description:
Dark Vengeance - Seattle’s darkest criminals force Elijah Kane and his hard knuckled team to track down a meticulous ‘Black Magic’-practicing killer in the vagrant strip club underworld. Kane seeks help in the form of criminologist Tanaka (George Takei), while Sarah Montgomery volunteers to work undercover, dancing in a strip joint known to be crawling with predators and low-lifes.
2010.  Stars: Steven Seagal, Sarah Lind, William 'Big Sleeps' Stewart, Meghan Ory, Warren Christie

metadata.Plot: Welcome to Planet Earth. It hos become o barren wasteland of greed and violence. A savage world of unspeakable cruelty. In a world torn by raging electrical storm's and ram pant with deadly cancers, there is only one escape: "the seeds" , a powerful hallucinogenic drug that provides great pleasure... and eventual madness. The Drug lords who control "the seeds" - control the planet, raping and killing all who stand in their way. Now one man must avenge his past to save the future in this story of survival, courage and determination...
